{"tid":1559232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"911 九龍塘區中學生人鏈","createTime":"2019-09-10T17:07:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T05:42:15.000Z","uid":201991,"like":29,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ae32d25a47c8795355aa692d68342a741d1c611c","tid":1559232,"uid":201991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iWmAaAX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiWmAaAX.jpg&h=d3f8ce28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽聞嚟緊911有16間分別嚟自觀塘、九龍塘以及將軍澳區嘅中學會起聯校人鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間：16.45-18.00<br />\n路線：雀橋街休憩處至到歌和老街公園<br />\n當中包含咗悼念911嘅環節，而且都會做唔少911相關嘅文宣<br />\n但小妹啱啱發現連登巴絲希望911暫停所有活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以諗住問問眾多位巴絲假如如期起人鏈嘅話支唔支持<br />\n正皮&mdash;&mdash;支持，繼續搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負皮&mdash;&mdash;不了，呢啲日子咁敏感，改期啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7f95ddf7f7a0bf17653c9fe8c5dad7aadd64d3","tid":1559232,"uid":201991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:07:23.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"883c8f4e1bae04c7da2a47bb8f2c00b119ed57fc","tid":1559232,"uid":201991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:07:34.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"7d124467957a444a80c33df5cfda232c4bbd2845","tid":1559232,"uid":201991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:08:33.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"3a0531618348b404f92e45d7df9db75b485fb2d4","tid":1559232,"uid":201991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"ba3186c8f10bfc130532f963b21be5a155016207","tid":1559232,"uid":201991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T17:11:27.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"25126eb363a55ac3108dcc76a737b61573d2d5a5","tid":1559232,"uid":201991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci